00:28:56,700 --> 00:28:58,540
- COOL. SO I'M JUST GONNA--

710
00:28:58,540 --> 00:29:00,580
I'M JUST GONNA TAKE
A BEAT HERE.

711
00:29:00,580 --> 00:29:02,580
YOU CAN GO.

712
00:29:02,580 --> 00:29:05,180
- BEEN TO THE CAFETERIA YET?
- NO.

713
00:29:05,180 --> 00:29:08,220
- FROZEN YOGURT'S
DO-IT-YOURSELF.

714
00:29:07,845 --> 00:29:12,005
NO LIMIT.

715
00:29:11,789 --> 00:29:15,429
- OKAY.

716
00:29:15,429 --> 00:29:16,549
- HEY, WHERE YOU GOING?

717
00:29:16,549 --> 00:29:18,229
- I GOT A PARTY
TO GO TO.

718
00:29:18,229 --> 00:29:19,789
CAN I HAVE MY PURSE, PLEASE?

719
00:29:19,789 --> 00:29:21,989
- YEAH. YOU KNOW,
THAT EYE'S GONNA SWELL UP.

720
00:29:21,989 --> 00:29:24,029
- OH, ARE YOU A DOCTOR?
YOU A DOCTOR COP?

721
00:29:24,029 --> 00:29:25,629
- NO, I JUST--
HOLD ON A SECOND.

722
00:29:25,629 --> 00:29:27,749
YOU JUST GOT ASSAULTED.

723
00:29:27,749 --> 00:29:30,229
- WHEN GOD SEES ME HAPPY
FOR ONE SECOND--

724
00:29:30,229 --> 00:29:32,149
- GOD HAS NOTHING TO DO WITH IT.
THAT WAS JUST SMALLS.

725
00:29:32,149 --> 00:29:34,429
- NO, NO, NO.
IT'S THIS NEIGHBORHOOD.

726
00:29:34,429 --> 00:29:36,069
MAN, I'M NEVER GETTING
OUT OF HERE.

727
00:29:36,069 --> 00:29:38,229
YOU KNOW MY BROTHER'S
IN A GANG?

728
00:29:38,229 --> 00:29:39,949
BET YOU ARRESTED HIM BEFORE.

729
00:29:39,949 --> 00:29:41,389
- THAT EXPLAINS
WHY YOU HATE COPS.

730
00:29:41,389 --> 00:29:42,909
- I AM NOT LETTING THAT THUG

731
00:29:42,909 --> 00:29:44,389
GET IN THE WAY OF MY PLANS,
ALL RIGHT?

732
00:29:44,389 --> 00:29:45,789
- OKAY, BUT LOOK,
YOU'RE SHAKING.

733
00:29:45,789 --> 00:29:48,349
TAKE A BREATH,
PULL YOURSELF TOGETHER.

734
00:29:48,349 --> 00:29:49,829
- I'M TOGETHER.

735
00:29:49,829 --> 00:29:51,029
DON'T I LOOK PRETTY?

736
00:29:51,029 --> 00:30:20,069
- YEAH.

737
00:30:20,069 --> 00:30:23,189
[elevator beeps]

738
00:30:23,189 --> 00:30:24,709
- HEY, IT'S ME.

739
00:30:24,709 --> 00:30:28,749
LISTEN,
I'M STILL AT THE HOSPITAL.

740
00:30:28,749 --> 00:30:31,709
YEAH, THERE WAS
A REALLY BIG CAR ACCIDENT,

741
00:30:31,709 --> 00:30:34,069
AND I JUST THINK
THAT BY THE TIME I GET DONE,

742
00:30:34,069 --> 00:30:36,069
MANHATTAN'S GONNA BE
TOO FAR TO GO.

743
00:30:36,069 --> 00:30:38,829
<i>[Kings of Leon's Use Somebody
playing]</i>

744
00:30:41,309 --> 00:30:45,149
[laughter]
- ARE YOU SERIOUS?

745
00:30:45,149 --> 00:30:47,549
- HEY, LOOK AT YOU,
ALL DRESSED UP.

746
00:30:47,549 --> 00:30:49,309
- STOP IT, GORILLA.

747
00:30:49,309 --> 00:30:50,709
- THANK YOU FOR INVITING US

748
00:30:50,709 --> 00:30:53,109
TO YOUR
NOT-GETTING-A-DIVORCE PARTY.

749
00:30:53,109 --> 00:30:54,829
- HERE YOU ARE, PRINCESS.

750
00:30:54,829 --> 00:30:56,429
- HEY, THERE'S MIKE.
HEY, MIKE!

751
00:30:56,429 --> 00:31:01,789
-  YOU AND ALL YOU KNOW
AND HOW YOU SPEAK

752
00:31:01,789 --> 00:31:04,749
all: OHH!

753
00:31:04,749 --> 00:31:07,229
- COME ON, COME ON, COME ON.

754
00:31:07,229 --> 00:31:08,909
- DRINK.
- COME ON, BIG BOY.

755
00:31:08,909 --> 00:31:10,829
- OH, MY GOD.
- WHO IS THAT?

756
00:31:10,829 --> 00:31:13,229
- OH, NO, NO, NO.
OFF LIMITS, GUYS.

757
00:31:13,229 --> 00:31:16,109
SHE'S FROM LANCASTER.
SHE'S PRACTICALLY AMISH.

758
00:31:16,109 --> 00:31:17,429
- RUMSPRINGA.

759
00:31:17,429 --> 00:31:20,189
- JUST DON'T TELL HER
I'M MARRIED, OKAY?

760
00:31:20,189 --> 00:31:22,389
- BUT HE'S TOO SKINNY.

761
00:31:22,389 --> 00:31:24,109
- OBAMA COULD KICK
PUTIN'S ASS.

762
00:31:24,109 --> 00:31:27,589
- ARE YOU HIGH?
PUTIN WAS K.G.B.

763
00:31:27,589 --> 00:31:30,989
HE COULD KILL YOU
WITH HIS BARE HANDS.

764
00:31:30,989 --> 00:31:35,229
UH...OH.

765
00:31:35,229 --> 00:31:37,789
THIS CAN'T BE GOOD.

766
00:31:37,789 --> 00:31:39,869
WE HAVE TO GO SEE
WHAT HAPPENED.

767
00:31:39,869 --> 00:31:41,709
- OH, CAN I COME, TOO?

768
00:31:41,709 --> 00:31:47,909
- WHAT DO YOU THINK
I MEANT BY "WE"?

769
00:31:47,909 --> 00:31:50,669
- HEY, MIKE,
CAN I BUM ONE OF THOSE?

770
00:31:50,669 --> 00:31:53,509
- THAT'S THE WORST THING
I'VE EVER HEARD.

771
00:31:53,509 --> 00:31:56,149
YOU HAVE TO BE CRUSHED.

772
00:31:56,149 --> 00:31:58,749
- LOOK, IT WAS NOT MY NIGHT.

773
00:31:58,749 --> 00:32:00,549
I'M NOT GONNA CRY
OVER IT, OKAY?

774
00:32:00,549 --> 00:32:02,269
- [sighs] OKAY.

775
00:32:02,269 --> 00:32:04,749
- WHAT?

776
00:32:04,749 --> 00:32:06,349
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

777
00:32:06,349 --> 00:32:09,189
I SHOULD HAVE NEVER LET YOU
HAVE ANY WHISKEY.

778
00:32:09,189 --> 00:32:12,709
- I COULDN'T EVEN LOOK
THAT KID'S MOTHER IN THE EYE.

779
00:32:12,709 --> 00:32:14,509
- IT'S ONLY YOUR FIRST WEEK.

780
00:32:14,509 --> 00:32:16,589
- [crying] I JUST...

781
00:32:16,589 --> 00:32:21,189
I PICTURED MYSELF
SAVING PEOPLE.

782
00:32:21,189 --> 00:32:24,629
HOW CAN I HELP ANYBODY
WHEN IT'S ALL SO SAD?

783
00:32:24,629 --> 00:32:26,589
- IT'S A JOB, ALL RIGHT?

784
00:32:26,589 --> 00:32:27,589
THAT'S ALL IT IS.

785
00:32:27,589 --> 00:32:29,229
- [sniffling]

786
00:32:29,229 --> 00:32:31,629
- YOU'RE THERE FOR PEOPLE DURING
THE WORST PART OF THEIR LIVES,

787
00:32:31,629 --> 00:32:33,549
YOU FIND A WAY
TO MAKE IT BETTER, AND THEN--

788
00:32:33,549 --> 00:32:36,469
AND THIS IS THE MOST
IMPORTANT PART, VERONICA--

789
00:32:36,469 --> 00:32:38,989
YOU LET IT GO.

790
00:32:38,989 --> 00:32:44,749
THAT'S HOW YOU
TAKE CARE OF YOURSELF.

791
00:32:44,749 --> 00:32:46,789
- WHAT?

792
00:32:46,789 --> 00:32:48,909
<i>I AM TAKING CARE OF ME.</i>

793
00:32:48,909 --> 00:32:50,309
WHAT DO YOU THINK

794
00:32:50,309 --> 00:32:52,989
GETTING BACK TOGETHER
WITH MIKE IS ALL ABOUT?

795
00:32:52,989 --> 00:32:54,469
HE'S A GOOD GUY, YOU KNOW?

796
00:32:54,469 --> 00:32:56,309
- YOU GOT A PROBLEM?

797
00:32:56,309 --> 00:32:58,389
- AND I REALLY THINK THIS IS
GONNA MAKE MY LIFE MORE STABLE.

798
00:32:58,389 --> 00:33:00,629
- YEAH, UM, WELL,
ACTUALLY MIKE'S DOWN THERE

799
00:33:00,629 --> 00:33:02,389
ABOUT TO GET HIS ASS KICKED.

800
00:33:02,389 --> 00:33:03,429
- WHAT?

801
00:33:03,429 --> 00:33:04,589
-  DO DO-DO-DO
DO-DO-DO

802
00:33:04,589 --> 00:33:05,629
DO DO-DO DO-DO

803
00:33:05,629 --> 00:33:07,989
DO DO-DO DO-DO DO 
- GET OFF!

804
00:33:07,989 --> 00:33:09,029
GET OFF OF HIM!

805
00:33:09,029 --> 00:33:10,309
-  DO DO-DO DO

806
00:33:10,309 --> 00:33:11,829
DO-DO DO DO-DO DO-DO DO 
- COME ON!

807
00:33:11,829 --> 00:33:14,229
DO DO-DO DO DO-DO DO

808
00:33:14,229 --> 00:33:18,509
DO-DO

809
00:33:18,509 --> 00:33:21,349
- YOU ARE TOO OLD TO BE
GETTING INTO FIGHTS, DUMMY.

810
00:33:21,349 --> 00:33:24,229
- IT WAS HIS FAULT.

811
00:33:24,229 --> 00:33:25,629
- DECIDED YOU DIDN'T NEED
A DOCTOR?

812
00:33:25,629 --> 00:33:28,229
- WELL, I DIDN'T LIKE
ANYBODY ON DUTY.

813
00:33:28,229 --> 00:33:29,709
MIKE, THIS IS DR. SANDS.

814
00:33:29,709 --> 00:33:33,029
DR. SANDS,
THIS IS MY HUSBAND MIKE.

815
00:33:33,029 --> 00:33:35,309
I WANT HIM
TO HAVE A CAT SCAN.

816
00:33:35,309 --> 00:33:37,029
- BARELY EVEN HURTS.

817
00:33:37,029 --> 00:33:38,349
- THAT'S BECAUSE YOU'RE DRUNK.

818
00:33:38,349 --> 00:33:39,749
YOU HIT THE CEMENT
WITH YOUR HEAD.

819
00:33:39,749 --> 00:33:40,669
YOU'RE GETTING A CAT SCAN.

820
00:33:40,669 --> 00:33:42,429
- TELL HER
I DON'T NEED NO SCAN.

821
00:33:42,429 --> 00:33:44,189
- WELL, LADY
SAYS YOU NEED A SCAN,

822
00:33:44,189 --> 00:33:46,149
YOU NEED A SCAN.

823
00:33:46,149 --> 00:33:47,829
COME ON,
WE'LL TAKE HIM UPSTAIRS.

824
00:33:47,829 --> 00:33:51,229
YOU'RE A LUCKY MAN.

825
00:33:51,229 --> 00:33:52,709
- I KNOW.

826
00:33:52,709 --> 00:33:55,309
I KNOW. [groans]

827
00:33:55,309 --> 00:33:58,709
SHE'S A BALL-BUSTER,
BUT I LOVE HER.

828
00:33:58,709 --> 00:34:00,429
HEY, YOU SHOULD HAVE
SEEN HER IN HIGH SCHOOL

829
00:34:00,429 --> 00:34:01,869
WHEN SHE WAS
IN HER GWEN STEFANI PHASE.

830
00:34:01,869 --> 00:34:06,349
- YEAH, OKAY.
ALL RIGHT, LET'S GO.

831
00:34:06,349 --> 00:34:07,789
- OOH, OOH, OOH.
- WHAT?

832
00:34:07,789 --> 00:34:09,669
NEXT WEEK.

833
00:34:09,669 --> 00:34:15,389
RIGHT. GOOD NIGHT.
BUDDY SYSTEM, BOYS.

834
00:34:15,389 --> 00:34:16,429
[bell rings]

835
00:34:16,429 --> 00:34:20,189
- LAST CALL!

836
00:34:20,189 --> 00:34:24,469
- HEY, MAN,
GIVE ME A SECOND.

837
00:34:24,475 --> 00:34:25,675
HEY, YOU.

838
00:34:25,675 --> 00:34:27,755
MY BUDDY, RYAN, INVITED
ME TO THIS PARTY,

839
00:34:27,755 --> 00:34:29,035
BUT IT LOOKS LIKE
I MISSED THE WHOLE THING.

840
00:34:29,035 --> 00:34:30,635
- YOU WANT TO GET OUT OF HERE?
- YES.

841
00:34:30,635 --> 00:34:33,715
-  UH-HUH, THERE'S NO PAPA
THAT CAN TREAT MY LIKE A LOVER

842
00:34:33,715 --> 00:34:36,275
WHO MAKES ME FEEL
SO RIGHT

843
00:34:36,275 --> 00:34:38,715
HIS LOVE IS SO TENDER,
IT MAKES ME SURRENDER

844
00:34:38,715 --> 00:34:40,395
WHEN HE SQUEEZE
AND HOLD ME TIGHT

845
00:34:40,070 --> 00:34:42,270
- YOU WANT A DRINK
OR SOMETHING?

846
00:34:42,270 --> 00:34:43,390
- STOP TALKING.

847
00:34:43,390 --> 00:35:05,750
-  THE WAY HE LOOKS
IN MY EYES

848
00:35:05,750 --> 00:35:08,790
- HEY.

849
00:35:08,790 --> 00:35:10,030
- HI.

850
00:35:10,030 --> 00:35:14,310
- I, UH,
GOT YOUR HUSBAND'S SCANS HERE.

851
00:35:14,310 --> 00:35:16,390
WANT TO COME TAKE A LOOK?

852
00:35:16,390 --> 00:35:21,390
- YEAH.

853
00:35:21,390 --> 00:35:23,750
- WELL, IT'S FINE.
THERE'S NO SWELLING.

854
00:35:23,750 --> 00:35:25,390
- YEAH, WELL,
HE'S GOT A HARD HEAD.

855
00:35:25,390 --> 00:35:29,150
- [laughs]

856
00:35:29,150 --> 00:35:31,670
HEY, HOW YOU SLEEPING?

857
00:35:31,670 --> 00:35:32,830
- BAD.

858
00:35:32,830 --> 00:35:35,550
- YEAH. ME, TOO.

859
00:35:35,550 --> 00:35:37,270
SO WEIRD BEING BACK.

860
00:35:37,270 --> 00:35:39,630
- YEAH.

861
00:35:39,630 --> 00:35:42,350
YEAH.

862
00:35:42,350 --> 00:35:46,990
IT'S LIKE THERE'S THIS WALL
BETWEEN ME AND EVERYBODY ELSE,

863
00:35:46,990 --> 00:35:50,630
AND THERE'S...
THERE'S ALL OF THIS STUFF

864
00:35:50,630 --> 00:35:53,830
THAT I CAN'T GET
OUT OF MY HEAD.

865
00:35:53,830 --> 00:35:57,910
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
IF I'M A GOOD NURSE ANYMORE,

866
00:35:57,910 --> 00:36:10,190
AND I FEEL LIKE I'M GONNA
BLOW UP ALL THE TIME.

867
00:36:10,190 --> 00:36:14,630
AND THEN THERE'S YOU.

868
00:36:14,630 --> 00:36:17,150
I FEEL LIKE I WOULD HAVE
GONE COMPLETELY CRAZY

869
00:36:17,150 --> 00:36:24,350
IF IT HADN'T BEEN FOR YOU.

870
00:36:24,350 --> 00:36:27,670
AND I FEEL LIKE I'VE...

871
00:36:27,670 --> 00:36:32,390
SORT OF BEEN CARRYING YOU
AROUND WITH ME.

872
00:36:32,390 --> 00:36:36,710
BUT I JUST--I...

873
00:36:36,710 --> 00:36:41,430
I FEEL LIKE I HAVE TO DO
THE RESPONSIBLE THING.

874
00:36:41,430 --> 00:36:43,390
- YEAH.

875
00:36:43,390 --> 00:36:46,670
I GUESS IT WAS,
UH, PRETTY STUPID OF ME

876
00:36:46,670 --> 00:36:50,910
TO COME RUNNING OUT HERE
FOR YOU.

877
00:36:50,910 --> 00:36:53,110
IT'S JUST THAT

878
00:36:53,110 --> 00:37:01,510
YOU WERE THE ONE THING
THAT MADE SENSE.

879
00:37:01,510 --> 00:37:03,230
- WHAT ARE YOU
GONNA DO NOW?

880
00:37:03,230 --> 00:37:05,430
- THERE'S NOTHING TO DO.

881
00:37:05,430 --> 00:37:08,790
I SIGNED
A TWO-YEAR CONTRACT.

882
00:37:08,790 --> 00:37:11,630
I'M STAYING.

883
00:37:11,630 --> 00:37:14,357
YOU CAN TAKE YOUR HUSBAND HOME
ANYTIME YOU LIKE.

884
00:37:28,116 --> 00:37:29,796
- I GUESS
WE'RE NOT HAVING BREAKFAST.

885
00:37:29,796 --> 00:37:32,316
- OH, UM...

886
00:37:32,316 --> 00:37:34,796
GOTTA GO TO WORK.

887
00:37:34,796 --> 00:37:43,316
BUT I'LL CALL YOU.

888
00:37:43,316 --> 00:37:45,716
- [knocks]

889
00:37:45,716 --> 00:37:47,476
TIME FOR YOUR MEDS.

890
00:37:47,476 --> 00:37:49,836
WHY IS YOUR HAIR
ON THE GROUND?

891
00:37:49,836 --> 00:37:54,236
- MY HEAD'S HOT. LEAVE IT.

892
00:37:54,236 --> 00:37:56,636
WHAT'S WITH YOU
AND THE SEXY SURGEON,

893
00:37:56,636 --> 00:37:58,516
THE ONE WHO SQUEEZED
YOUR ARM LAST NIGHT?

894
00:37:58,516 --> 00:38:00,796
- YOU LOOKED
LIKE YOU WERE ASLEEP.

895
00:38:00,796 --> 00:38:02,596
- UNBELIEVABLE.

896
00:38:02,596 --> 00:38:04,156
MY DAUGHTER'S ONLINE DATING,

897
00:38:04,156 --> 00:38:05,876
AND YOU WITH TWO MEN
AFTER YOU.

898
00:38:05,876 --> 00:38:07,396
- YEAH, WE WERE
IN THE WAR TOGETHER.

899
00:38:07,396 --> 00:38:09,236
TAKE YOUR PILLS.

900
00:38:09,236 --> 00:38:12,396
- WAR? HOW SWEEPING
AND ROMANTIC.

901
00:38:12,396 --> 00:38:13,836
I HOPE YOU DON'T THINK

902
00:38:13,836 --> 00:38:15,636
A MAN'S GONNA FIX
WHATEVER'S WRONG WITH YOU.

903
00:38:15,636 --> 00:38:20,916
- JUST SWALLOW THE DRUGS,
LADY.

904
00:38:20,916 --> 00:38:32,156
- YOU THINK I SHOULD
HAVE THIS SURGERY?

905
00:38:32,156 --> 00:38:38,156
- YOU KNOW...

906
00:38:38,156 --> 00:38:39,516
IF YOU WERE MY MOTHER...

907
00:38:39,516 --> 00:38:43,236
- YOU'D HAVE A BETTER HAIRCUT.

908
00:38:43,236 --> 00:38:47,596
- UM, IF YOU WERE MY MOTHER,

909
00:38:47,596 --> 00:38:51,276
I WOULD SAY NO.

910
00:38:51,276 --> 00:38:53,716
IT'S TOO RISKY,
AND IT PROBABLY WON'T WORK.

911
00:38:53,716 --> 00:38:58,116
- I'M DYING.

912
00:38:58,116 --> 00:39:01,476
- YEAH.

913
00:39:01,476 --> 00:39:06,676
YEAH, YOU ARE.

914
00:39:06,676 --> 00:39:08,436
THERE ARE A COUPLE OF THINGS
THAT SCARE ME

915
00:39:08,436 --> 00:39:11,196
ABOUT THIS SURGERY.

916
00:39:11,196 --> 00:39:13,476
YOU COULD DIE
ON THE OPERATING TABLE.

917
00:39:13,476 --> 00:39:15,996
AT LEAST
THAT WOULD BE PAINLESS.

918
00:39:15,996 --> 00:39:19,836
OR YOU COULD DIE
IN RECOVERY,

919
00:39:19,836 --> 00:39:25,996
IN PAIN AND ON A VENTILATOR,
AND THAT SCARES ME.

920
00:39:25,996 --> 00:39:27,436
I THINK THAT YOU NEED
TO DECIDE

921
00:39:27,436 --> 00:39:34,236
ON THE QUALITY OF TIME
YOU HAVE LEFT.

922
00:39:34,236 --> 00:39:37,396
AND I'M--I'M SCARING
THE HELL OUT OF YOU RIGHT NOW,

923
00:39:37,396 --> 00:39:39,796
WHICH IS WHY IT'S BECOMING
VERY CLEAR TO ME

924
00:39:39,796 --> 00:39:41,796
I AM IN THE WRONG LINE
OF WORK.

925
00:39:41,796 --> 00:39:44,316
- NO.

926
00:39:44,316 --> 00:39:47,756
YOU'RE THE ONLY PERSON
WHO'S BEEN HONEST WITH ME.

927
00:39:47,756 --> 00:39:54,116
PEOPLE TREAT YOU LIKE
AN IMBECILE WHEN YOU'RE SICK.

928
00:39:54,116 --> 00:39:59,116
- IF YOU WANT
TO STOP TREATMENT...

929
00:39:59,116 --> 00:40:02,236
ALL YOU HAVE TO DO
IS SAY SO.

930
00:40:02,236 --> 00:40:06,196
YOUR KIDS WILL UNDERSTAND.

931
00:40:06,196 --> 00:40:20,316
- I THINK I'D LIKE TO BE ALONE,
IF THAT'S ALL RIGHT.

932
00:40:20,316 --> 00:40:23,396
VERONICA,
YOU'RE A WONDERFUL NURSE.

933
00:40:23,396 --> 00:40:37,956
DON'T DOUBT IT
FOR A SECOND.

934
00:40:37,956 --> 00:40:39,996
- SHE'S BEEN HERE ALL NIGHT.

935
00:40:39,996 --> 00:40:43,036
I'VE BEEN TRYING TO KEEP
THE TRANSPLANT VULTURES AT BAY.

936
00:40:43,036 --> 00:40:45,636
- DOES SHE HAVE ANY FAMILY
OR ANYTHING?

937
00:40:45,636 --> 00:40:47,276
- I DON'T KNOW.

938
00:40:47,276 --> 00:40:49,076
HAVEN'T SEEN ANYONE ELSE.

939
00:40:49,076 --> 00:40:52,396
JUST HER.

940
00:40:52,396 --> 00:40:55,396
<i>[The Kills'
